,"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"앗…… 저기에 계신 분은 설마…… \n타츠미 씨! 좋은 아침이에요!!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event154-07-003","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":221}],"windowDisplayName":"타츠미","body":"좋은 아침은 무슨, 또 너희구만. \n갑자기 말 걸지 마.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":221,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":221,"voiceId":"event154-07-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"타츠미 씨, 저기, 혹시…… \n저희를 배웅하러 온 건가요?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event154-07-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":221}],"windowDisplayName":"타츠미","body":"아니거든요~ 비행기를 배웅하러 왔거든요~ \n슈웅 날아가는 비행기를 배웅하러 왔거든요~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":221,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":221,"voiceId":"event154-07-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"아하핫♪ 뭐야 그게~ \n타츠미 씨는 정말 특이하다니까.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event154-07-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":221}],"windowDisplayName":"타츠미","body":"너희 같은 도시 사람한테 듣고 싶지 않거든.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":221,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":221,"voiceId":"event154-07-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":1,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":221}],"windowDisplayName":"타츠미","body":"「억수로 억수로 축제」 꽤 좋았어. \n사가 사람들이 진심으로 즐거워하는 모습을 볼 수 있었지. \n와준 건…… 조금은 감사하더군.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":221,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":221,"voiceId":"event154-07-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"치사토","body":"타츠미 씨…… ","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"event154-07-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":20}],"windowDisplayName":"이브","body":"저기…… 그때는 무례하다고 했지만\n타츠미 씨가 잘못을 지적해 주셔서 다행이에요. \n감사합니다!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":20,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":20,"voiceId":"event154-07-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":19}],"windowDisplayName":"마야","body":"정말입니다. 한때는 걱정 많이 했지만 \n사가에서 일할 수 있어서 좋았습니다.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":19,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":19,"voiceId":"event154-07-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":17}],"windowDisplayName":"히나","body":"응응, 재밌는 곳도 갔으니까~♪ \n사가는 꽤 룽♪ 한 곳이 많았어~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":17,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":17,"voiceId":"event154-07-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":16}],"windowDisplayName":"아야","body":"스태프 분한테 들었는데 저희가 좀비인 걸 들켰을 때\n「라이브를 멈추지 마」라고 한 사람이 있다고 하셨어요…… \n그거 타츠미 씨 맞으시죠?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":16,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":16,"voiceId":"event154-07-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":221}],"windowDisplayNa